accessibility.text: It turns out to be a bad dream.
The sound of your annoying phone clock is indicating that it's time to get up for the first day of school.
\"What a strange dream.\" You shrug your shoulders and walk to the bathroom, not noticing that there is a giant soft ribbon passing by your bedroom window, just like the tendril of a jellyfish.

After breakfast, the clock shows it's already 7:55 in the morning. \"Oh great, I'm going to be late for class again on the first day of school, like always.\" You grab your backpack and rush out to the door.
